For my project, I plan to create an interactive clock that lives in a web browser. The design will be inspired by a tire wheel because a tire has the same circular shape as a clock. As a tire spins, its movement is similar to the way the hour and minute hands rotate around a clock face. My website will use this connection between shape and motion by making the tire function as the clock.
The clock will display the current time with animated hour and minute hands. I also want to include moving visual effects, such as subtle animations or flashing graphics, to reinforce the theme of movement. The website will have two pages: an index.html page that contains the interactive clock and an about.html page that explains the concept, design process, and references used in the project.
