References:
Seeker by Leon Cmielewski – The first reference inspired me to add projected or animated visual effects in my project to emphasize the movement and make the clock feel more dynamic: https://www.digiart21.org/art/seeker
The Clock Clock Project - This second reference helped me conceptualize how to make a clock dynamic as well. The sleek but dynamic design for this clock project, and its concept, really interested me and got me thinking about what time can represent: https://www.humanssince1982.com/en-us/blogs/concepts/the-clock-clock-2008-2010 
